  Locus:
    Page: 436
    Verse: 4
Tags:
  - Smile
---
You find yourself refreshed by the presence of cheerful people. Why not
make earnest effort to confer that pleasure on others? Half the battle is
gained if you never allow yourself to say anything gloomy.
